{"lang": "zh_CN", "eventid": "act50side", "eventName": "泡影苍霆", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "TD-3", "avgTag": "行动后", "storyName": "不能掉以轻心", "storyInfo": "梓兰和空爆换好装备后，和宝巫迦一同出发，前往狩猎“异兽”。出发前，一行人开开心心地吃了一顿炎火村特产——兔团子。", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "紧急任务", "x": 250.0, "y": 200.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 750.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n委托人     「泡影国国主——宝巫迦」", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "任务描述", "x": 250.0, "y": 200.0, "alignment": "left", "size": 24.0, "delay": 0.04, "width": 750.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n据月见夜将军的手下回报，雪山出现了异变，推断是由“异兽”造成的影响。", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n“异兽”乃是泡影国的宿命之敌，若不尽早狩猎，一旦“诅咒”蔓延，后果不堪设想......", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n请“异兽猎人”即刻随吾出征，完成对本轮“异兽”的狩猎！", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "multi": "true", "text": "\\n\\n任务报酬    归乡之途", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Sticker", "attributes": {"id": "st1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g4_bambooforest", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 4.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$path_intro", "key": "$path_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“异兽猎人”空爆，准备出发！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "该带的东西都带好了吧？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "让我看看，帐篷、携带食料、钓竿、望远镜、十字镐、捕虫网、烤肉组合——", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#1$1"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "报告，都带好了！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_knockhead_cartoon", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.4, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们不是去玩探险游戏的！", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#2"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还有，你是从哪里搞来这些东西的？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "都是这两天城里的好心人们给我的，我们毕竟也算英雄嘛，大家对我可好了。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且这些都是很有用的狩猎道具！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是搞不懂这些东西对狩猎“异兽”有什么帮助。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#2"}, {"id": 44, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "先熟悉周围的环境和地形再进行狩猎也不失为一种选择。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 46, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "异变怎么样了？", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "根据斥候的情报，走在雪山中，时不时会感受到热浪的存在......", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#6$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这毫无疑问是“异兽”的杰作。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#9$1"}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但两位也不必急于一时，就目前而言，异变看起来还没有从雪山蔓延开。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 54, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还是趁早解决吧。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 56, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且我看宝巫迦已经忍不住啦！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#9$1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......吾没有忍不住。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你手里的斧子还有你的眼神不是这么说的哦，宝巫迦。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#8$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不过，有一件事我很好奇，狩猎真的需要来这么多人吗？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#8$1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我还以为只是我、梓兰姐和宝巫迦的事呢。", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#8$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "当然喵，这不是简单的狩猎，当然是人越多越好喵！", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$7", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有我给你们当向导，事半功倍喵！", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$7"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "还有这家伙喵！", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyD_1#1$1", "afrom": 0.0, "ato": 1.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好威风的牙兽！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#5$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyD_1#1$5", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_dog_voice1", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（威胁的低吼）", "name": "义经"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyD_1#1$5"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，别这么凶嘛！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他是——", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#3"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他不太放心你们喵！", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我们会跟着你们行动喵。", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "将军呢，将军不会打算跟吾等一起行动吧？", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#1$1"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陛下放心，我当然相信陛下。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#6$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这段时间，斥候们在竹林中发现了许多受“诅咒”侵染的野兽们互相残杀的痕迹。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#6$1"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这不太寻常，我打算带队亲自收集一些情报。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#6$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是顺路来为陛下送行而已。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心吧，只要陛下狩猎的目标不改变，我不会对您的狩猎进行任何干涉。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 100, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吾现在就想把狩猎的目标换成你......", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#9$1"}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那也未尝不可。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#5$1"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哼。", "name": "宝巫迦"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2100_1#4$1"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那么，陛下，祝您狩猎顺利。", "name": "月见夜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2101_1#1$1"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "斑弥罗呢，你要跟我们一起去吗？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#1$1"}, {"id": 114, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我才懒得去。", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不是要给你们送装备，我连门都懒得出。", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快点换上试试吧，为了加紧给你们打造这两套装备，我可是一晚上没睡，累死我了。", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我要回去补觉了。", "name": "斑弥罗"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_2103_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘻嘻，新装备，新装备！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_282_catap_1#3$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "char_278_orchid_1#1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "char_278_orchid_1#1"}, {"id": 127, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "71_i02", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScale": 1.1, "yScale": 1.1}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "ImageTween", "attributes": {"image": "24_i05", "fadetime": 1.0, "xScaleFrom": 1.1, "yScaleFrom": 1.1, "xScaleTo": 1.0, "yScaleTo": 1.0, "duration": 20.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇哦，梓兰姐，这套衣服穿上真的好合身啊。", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "废话，设计图是我亲手改过的，要是不合身，就一定是斑弥罗的手艺有问题。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那斑弥罗的手艺还不错嘛。", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "算是吧。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "穿上新装备的感觉如何喵？", "name": "政宗"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......好像感觉身体轻盈了一些，而且，力量似乎也有所提高。", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "确实......虽然这种感觉很微妙，不过，的确能感觉到力量......这到底是什么原理？", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是特殊的锻造技艺喵！", "name": "政宗"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "总之对狩猎有好处喵！", "name": "政宗"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也就是说你其实也不懂吧。", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_dog_voice1", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（赞同的低吼）", "name": "义经"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice3", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "才不是喵！我是隐秘队的成员，又不是加工商的学徒喵！不知道很正常喵！", "name": "政宗"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔哦，这就是我的新武器吗！", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没错，这和你之前顺手拿的那把可不一样喵！是真正为了狩猎而存在的武器喵！", "name": "政宗"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿嘿......我现在好想砍点什么东西啊。", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "义经，就决定是你了！", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_dog_voice2", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（不屑的低吼）", "name": "义经"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "梓兰，来试着射中我头上的苹果喵！", "name": "政宗"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_caxe_creek", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈，梓兰姐嘴上说着对狩猎不感兴趣，结果还是兴致勃勃的嘛。", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然我要用这把弓，我当然要好好用它。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "反倒是你，别又和平时一样三分钟热度，过一会儿又喊着要换武器。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不会的啦！", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我有预感，盾斧就是我命中注定的武器！", "name": "空爆"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "它最好是。", "name": "梓兰"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在简单的适应过后，两人没有过多停留，就和宝巫迦踏上了出发的道路。"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "空爆的心中，满是对前程的期待，她对新的武器十分感兴趣，发自内心地希望能够挑战更强大的对手。"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而梓兰则一如往常地满怀忧愁，她知道，前方等待着她们的，绝不是轻松的战斗。"}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不过，至少经过自己调整的这套新的装备在外观上十分符合她的审美，这稍稍让她高兴了一点。"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "71_g4_bambooforest", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "对了，还有一件事要做喵！", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$2"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什么事？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#1$2"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下来可能随时要面临战斗了喵。", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$2"}, {"id": 193, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然要战斗，不吃一顿属于猎人的大餐可不行喵！", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#9$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什么，有大餐吃？！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#9$2"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$7", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "没错喵！", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$7"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我来请你们吃炎火村的名产——", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#4$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "什么，会有很好吃的肉吗！", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#4$2"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$7", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“兔团子”喵！", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$7"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1049_catap2_1#14$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸——说到猎人的大餐，难道不应该大口吃肉、大口喝酒吗？", "name": "空爆"}, "figure_art": "avg_1049_catap2_1#14$2"}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#8$2", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "甜点......我就免了。", "name": "梓兰"}, "figure_art": "avg_1048_orchd2_1#8$2"}, {"id": 210, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$3", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "这是偏见喵！", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$3"}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$MHR_cat_voice1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "吃了团子你们就知错了喵！", "name": "政宗"}, "figure_art": "avg_4215_buddyC_1#1$1"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}